#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn12.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Buddhavagga "
msgstr "1. The Buddhas "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Gotamasutta → mahā sakyamuni gotamo (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Gotamasutta "
msgstr "10. Gotama "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.10, sc1
msgctxt "sn12.10:1.1"
msgid "“Pubbeva me, bhikkhave, sambodhā anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva sato etadahosi: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, before my awakening—when I was still unawakened but intent on awakening—I thought: "

msgctxt "sn12.10:1.2"
msgid "‘kicchaṃ vatāyaṃ loko āpanno jāyati ca jīyati ca mīyati ca cavati ca upapajjati ca. "
msgstr "‘Alas, this world has fallen into trouble. It’s born, grows old, dies, passes away, and is reborn, "

msgctxt "sn12.10:1.3"
msgid "Atha ca panimassa dukkhassa nissaraṇaṃ nappajānāti jarāmaraṇassa. "
msgstr "yet it doesn’t understand how to escape from this suffering, from old age and death. "

msgctxt "sn12.10:1.4"
msgid "Kudāssu nāma imassa dukkhassa nissaraṇaṃ paññāyissati jarāmaraṇassā’ti? "
msgstr "Oh, when will an escape be found from this suffering, from old age and death?’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn12.10:2.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then it occurred to me: "

msgctxt "sn12.10:2.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati jarāmaraṇaṃ hoti, kiṃpaccayā jarāmaraṇan’ti? "
msgstr "‘When what exists is there old age and death? What is a condition for old age and death?’ "

msgctxt "sn12.10:2.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya abhisamayo: "
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, I comprehended with wisdom: "

msgctxt "sn12.10:2.4"
msgid "‘jātiyā kho sati jarāmaraṇaṃ hoti, jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇan’ti. "
msgstr "‘When rebirth exists there’s old age and death. Rebirth is a condition for old age and death.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn12.10:3.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then it occurred to me: "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati jāti hoti … pe … "
msgstr "‘When what exists is there rebirth? … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.3"
msgid "bhavo … "
msgstr "continued existence … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.4"
msgid "upādānaṃ … "
msgstr "grasping … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.5"
msgid "taṇhā … "
msgstr "craving … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.6"
msgid "vedanā … "
msgstr "feeling … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.7"
msgid "phasso … "
msgstr "contact … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.8"
msgid "saḷāyatanaṃ … "
msgstr "the six sense fields … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.9"
msgid "nāmarūpaṃ … "
msgstr "name and form … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.10"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ … "
msgstr "consciousness … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.11"
msgid "saṅkhārā honti, kiṃpaccayā saṅkhārā’ti? "
msgstr "‘When what exists are there choices? What is a condition for choices?’ "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.12"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya abhisamayo: "
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, I comprehended with wisdom: "

msgctxt "sn12.10:3.13"
msgid "‘avijjāya kho sati saṅkhārā honti, avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā’ti. "
msgstr "‘When ignorance exists there are choices. Ignorance is a condition for choices.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn12.10:4.1"
msgid "Iti hidaṃ avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā; "
msgstr "And so, ignorance is a condition for choices. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.10:4.2"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness. … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:4.3"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates. "

msgctxt "sn12.10:4.4"
msgid "‘Samudayo, samudayo’ti kho me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi. "
msgstr "‘Origination, origination.’ Such was the vision, knowledge, wisdom, realization, and light that arose in me regarding teachings not learned before from another. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn12.10:5.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then it occurred to me: "

msgctxt "sn12.10:5.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho asati jarāmaraṇaṃ na hoti, kissa nirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho’ti? "
msgstr "‘When what doesn’t exist is there no old age and death? When what ceases do old age and death cease?’ "

msgctxt "sn12.10:5.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya abhisamayo: "
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, I comprehended with wisdom: "

msgctxt "sn12.10:5.4"
msgid "‘jātiyā kho asati jarāmaraṇaṃ na hoti, jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho’ti. "
msgstr "‘When rebirth doesn’t exist there’s no old age and death? When rebirth ceases, old age and death cease.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.11, sc6
msgctxt "sn12.10:6.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then it occurred to me: "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho asati jāti na hoti … pe … "
msgstr "‘When what doesn’t exist is there no rebirth? … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.3"
msgid "bhavo … "
msgstr "continued existence … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.4"
msgid "upādānaṃ … "
msgstr "grasping … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.5"
msgid "taṇhā … "
msgstr "craving … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.6"
msgid "vedanā … "
msgstr "feeling … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.7"
msgid "phasso … "
msgstr "contact … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.8"
msgid "saḷāyatanaṃ … "
msgstr "the six sense fields … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.9"
msgid "nāmarūpaṃ … "
msgstr "name and form … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.10"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ … "
msgstr "consciousness … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.11"
msgid "saṅkhārā na honti, kissa nirodhā saṅkhāranirodho’ti? "
msgstr "‘When what doesn’t exist are there no choices? When what ceases do choices cease?’ "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.12"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya abhisamayo: "
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, I comprehended with wisdom: "

msgctxt "sn12.10:6.13"
msgid "‘avijjāya kho asati saṅkhārā na honti, avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho’ti. "
msgstr "‘When ignorance doesn’t exist there are no choices. When ignorance ceases, choices cease.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn12.10:7.1"
msgid "Iti hidaṃ avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho; "
msgstr "And so, when ignorance ceases, choices cease. "

msgctxt "sn12.10:7.2"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe … "
msgstr "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. … "

msgctxt "sn12.10:7.3"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases. "

msgctxt "sn12.10:7.4"
msgid "‘Nirodho, nirodho’ti kho me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādī”ti. "
msgstr "‘Cessation, cessation.’ Such was the vision, knowledge, wisdom, realization, and light that arose in me regarding teachings not learned before from another.” "

msgctxt "sn12.10:7.5"
msgid "Dasamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.10:7.6"
msgid "Buddhavaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn12.10:8.1"
msgid "Desanā vibhaṅgapaṭipadā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.10:8.2"
msgid "Vipassī sikhī ca vessabhū; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.10:8.3"
msgid "Kakusandho koṇāgamano kassapo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.10:8.4"
msgid "Mahāsakyamuni ca gotamoti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
